{"title":"Mongolia 100","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Mongolia 100","page-layout":"full","toc":false},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"mongolia-shell\">\n  <section class=\"hero-panel\">\n    <div class=\"hero-copy\">\n      <p class=\"eyebrow\">Daily Mongolia Fact Game</p>\n      <h1>Mongolia 100</h1>\n      <p class=\"hero-text\">\n        Work through 100 Mongolia facts, keep your streak alive, and clear the full trail\n        without seeing the same question twice in one cycle.\n      </p>\n      <div class=\"hero-chips\">\n        <span class=\"chip\">100 fact cards</span>\n        <span class=\"chip\">No repeats in a run</span>\n        <span class=\"chip\">Streak saved locally</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"hero-side\">\n      <div class=\"date-badge\" id=\"todayBadge\">Loading today's trail...</div>\n      <a class=\"fact-link-card\" href=\"all-games.html\">\n        <p class=\"mini-label\">All games</p>\n        <h2>Browse the game hub and future releases.</h2>\n        <p class=\"motif-note\">Use the launcher page to jump between live games and upcoming slots.</p>\n      </a>\n      <a class=\"fact-link-card\" href=\"about.html\">\n        <p class=\"mini-label\">Fact archive</p>\n        <h2>Browse all 100 facts on a separate page.</h2>\n        <p class=\"motif-note\">Use the archive if you want to study before or after a streak run.</p>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"stats-strip\">\n    <article class=\"stat-card\">\n      <p class=\"stat-label\">Current streak</p>\n      <p class=\"stat-value\" id=\"streakValue\">0</p>\n    </article>\n    <article class=\"stat-card\">\n      <p class=\"stat-label\">Best streak</p>\n      <p class=\"stat-value\" id=\"bestValue\">0</p>\n    </article>\n    <article class=\"stat-card\">\n      <p class=\"stat-label\">Progress this cycle</p>\n      <p class=\"stat-value\" id=\"progressValue\">0 / 100</p>\n    </article>\n    <article class=\"stat-card\">\n      <p class=\"stat-label\">Cards left</p>\n      <p class=\"stat-value\" id=\"remainingValue\">100</p>\n    </article>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"play-grid\">\n    <article class=\"game-panel\">\n      <div class=\"question-meta\">\n        <span class=\"meta-pill\" id=\"categoryPill\">Category</span>\n        <span class=\"meta-pill subtle\" id=\"questionIndexPill\">Card 1</span>\n      </div>\n      <h2 id=\"questionText\">Loading question...</h2>\n      <p class=\"question-lead\" id=\"questionLead\">\n        Pick the best answer. Correct answers grow your streak. Wrong answers reset the streak,\n        but the card still retires so you will not see it again in the same run.\n      </p>\n      <div class=\"options-grid\" id=\"optionsGrid\"></div>\n      <div class=\"feedback-panel\" id=\"feedbackPanel\" hidden>\n        <p class=\"feedback-result\" id=\"feedbackResult\"></p>\n        <p class=\"feedback-fact\" id=\"feedbackFact\"></p>\n        <button class=\"primary-button\" id=\"continueButton\" type=\"button\">Next fact</button>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"panel-actions\">\n        <button class=\"ghost-button\" id=\"restartButton\" type=\"button\">Restart cycle</button>\n      </div>\n    </article>\n\n    <aside class=\"info-panel\">\n      <h3>How it works</h3>\n      <ul class=\"rules-list\">\n        <li>Each cycle uses all 100 fact cards once.</li>\n        <li>Cards never repeat inside a cycle, even after a wrong answer.</li>\n        <li>Your streak counts only consecutive correct answers.</li>\n        <li>Finishing the deck makes you the winner and unlocks a restart prompt.</li>\n        <li>A fresh reshuffle starts the next time you restart a completed run.</li>\n      </ul>\n      <div class=\"mini-panel\">\n        <p class=\"mini-label\">Current run</p>\n        <p id=\"runSummary\">Preparing the question trail...</p>\n      </div>\n    </aside>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"source-panel\">\n    <p class=\"eyebrow\">Source Notes</p>\n    <p>\n      Fact prompts were compiled from general reference material on Mongolia, including\n      Britannica, UNESCO listings, the CIA World Factbook, and Mongolia-focused culture and\n      travel references. The game presents them as short quiz cards rather than quoted source text.\n    </p>\n  </section>\n</div>\n\n<dialog id=\"winnerDialog\" class=\"winner-dialog\">\n  <div class=\"winner-content\">\n    <p class=\"eyebrow\">Trail Complete</p>\n    <h2>You cleared all 100 Mongolia facts.</h2>\n    <p id=\"winnerMessage\">\n      Your current cycle is complete. Restart to reshuffle the deck and play again.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"winner-actions\">\n      <button class=\"primary-button\" id=\"winnerRestartButton\" type=\"button\">Restart trail</button>\n      <button class=\"ghost-button\" id=\"winnerCloseButton\" type=\"button\">View fact archive</button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</dialog>\n\n\n<script src=\"game.js\"></script>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"mongolia-shell\">\n  <section class=\"hero-panel\">\n    <div class=\"hero-copy\">\n      <p class=\"eyebrow\">Daily Mongolia Fact Game</p>\n      <h1>Mongolia 100</h1>\n      <p class=\"hero-text\">\n        Work through 100 Mongolia facts, keep your streak alive, and clear the full trail\n        without seeing the same question twice in one cycle.\n      </p>\n      <div class=\"hero-chips\">\n        <span class=\"chip\">100 fact cards</span>\n        <span class=\"chip\">No repeats in a run</span>\n        <span class=\"chip\">Streak saved locally</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"hero-side\">\n      <div class=\"date-badge\" id=\"todayBadge\">Loading today's trail...</div>\n      <a class=\"fact-link-card\" href=\"all-games.html\">\n        <p class=\"mini-label\">All games</p>\n        <h2>Browse the game hub and future releases.</h2>\n        <p class=\"motif-note\">Use the launcher page to jump between live games and upcoming